    <h1>Help: IT Ticketing System</h1>
    <p>This guide will help you navigate and use the Ticklr Ticketing System effectively.</p>

    <hr />

    <h2>Submitting a Ticket</h2>
    <p>Log in to the ticket system.</p>
    <p>Select <strong>"Create a Ticket"</strong> from the dashboard.</p>
    <p>Fill in the required fields (Description, Category, and Priority).</p>
    <p>Click <strong>"Create"</strong> to submit the ticket.</p>

    <h2>Viewing Your Tickets</h2>
    <p>Click on <strong>"View Past Tickets"</strong> from the dashboard.</p>
    <p>Select any ticket to view its status or edit if necessary.</p>

    <h2>Editing a Ticket</h2>
    <p>From your ticket list, click the <strong>"Edit"</strong> button next to a ticket.</p>
    <p>Update the relevant fields and click <strong>"Save"</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Closing a Ticket</h2>
    <p>Open the ticket that has been resolved.</p>
    <p>Check the <strong>"Is Completed"</strong> box and save the changes.</p>

